peopleAlsoAsk.question: Do vintage McDonald's glasses have lead?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: In short: McDonald's new 2024 collector cups are made of plastic, unlike earlier glass versions. Past McDonald's glassware, including 2010 Shrek glasses, was recalled due to toxic cadmium levels. Lead contamination in older cups has been a long-standing issue, with some testing far above legal safety limits.
